Package de.feu.showgo.ui.actions

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CopyEnsembleAction
    This action executes the copy ensemble action.
    DeleteEnsembleAction
    This action deletes the provided ensemble from the showgo singleton.
    DeletePersonAction
    This action deletes the provided person from the showgo singleton.
    DeleteProductionAction
    This action deletes the provided production from the showgo singleton.
    EditEnsembleAction
    This action opens the edit ensemble view with the provided ensemble.
    EditPersonAction
    This action open the edit person view with the provided person.
    EditProductionAction
    This action opens the edit production view with the provided production.
    LoadAction
    This action shows a file dialog and loads the selected .showgo save file.
    NewAction
    This action creates a new showgo singleton, discarding the current one.
    SaveAction
    This action saves the showgo singleton to the current save file.
    SaveAsAction
    This action displays a save file dialog and writes the showgo singleton into the selected file.
    ShowCreatePersonAction
    This action displays the CreatePerson view.
    ShowEnsembleViewAction
    This action displays to the ensemble view.
    ShowPlaybillAction
    This action displays the playbill view for a provided production.
    ShowProductionViewAction
    This action displays the production view.
    ShowReadPlayAction
    This action displays the read play view.
    ViewEnsembleAction
    This action displays the edit ensemble view in read only mode.
